ng shift log books, reconciliation documents, float records, and other admi=
nistrative records</li><li>Performing other related duties as assigned<br><=
br></li></ul><strong>Requirements<br><br></strong><strong>Minimum Qualifica=
tions:<br><br></strong>Five (5) subject passes equivalent to G.C.E. Ordinar=
