<br><strong>Skills &amp; Attributes<br><br></strong><ul><li>Good communicat=
ion skills</li><li>Accuracy</li><li>Strong attention to detail</li><li>Abil=
ity to learn and apply technical aviation-related procedures</li><li>A high=
 level of responsibility and confidentiality<br><br></li></ul><strong>Addit=
