and is comfortable taking ownership of essential operational and administra=
tive tasks. You will work closely with clinical sites, vendors, and interna=
l team members to ensure smooth study execution and compliance with regulat=
ory and company standards.</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Key Respon=
