nd removing users as needed.</li><li>Prepare, distribute, and archive meeti=
ng minutes, agendas, and other study documentation.</li><li>Support the dev=
elopment, organization, and maintenance of Trial Master File (TMF) document=
ation.</li><li>Perform general administrative and operational tasks to supp=
ort the Clinical Operations team and overall study execution.</li></ul><p><=
